CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS passwordResetTokens (
  id int AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  userId int NOT NULL,
  token varchar(255) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  expiresAt timestamp NOT NULL,
  usedAt timestamp,
  createdAt timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
);
